<plot>THE FINISHING LINE tells the story of Noel Martin, who was brutally attacked by Neo-Nazis becoming quadriplegic. Three years ago his dream came true: His racehorse won at Royal Ascot and he became the first triumphant black owner. Although his horse will race again, he has decided to get Euthanasia! THE FINISHING LINE explores Noel Martins desire to end it all and what drives him on.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?557796</url></doc>
